Package edu.cmu.commons.guice.convert

Interface Summary
TypeConversion Combines Matcher and TypeConverter interfaces.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTypeConversion Helper class for TypeConversion implementations.
PropertyEditorTypeConversion Support conversion from String to any type for which a PropertyEditor can be found via PropertyEditorManager.findEditor(Class).
StringConstructorTypeConversion Support conversion from String to any type which defines a constructor accepting a single String argument, for instance File.File(String).
TypeConversionExtensionsModule Include this Module when building your Injector to automatically register all type converters provided by this package:
